 class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想有d小本生意搞下<br />\n<br />\n有資金唔知做咩</blockquote><br />\n熟嗰樣做嗰樣囉<br />\n我見我啲朋友，唔熟但請人做，仆得仲死過我<br />\n自己熟嗰樣，先知成個流程，可以設計到最有市場價值嘅產品或者服務"},{"pid":"4367a528a12967720903923bb28e11fb1a660f1a","tid":437963,"uid":73914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"留意細節好緊要 同埋要用心"},{"pid":"49e3d5186e2e57c315f3fcf047f94c9ef69103fa","tid":437963,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全無生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜就唔講喇<br />\n又無乜錢宣傳，第一次搞好多嘢無計到</blockquote><br />\n小本生意客源真係最重要<br />\n巴打點撐<br />\n我自己資金都有限<br />\n做嗰行屬於冷門生意<br />\n暫時最有效係google 關鍵字<br />\n賣forum 廣告、派傳單都試過零作用"},{"pid":"741e0e815955a0d2bd3be08ed91aac16f0847c33","tid":437963,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時ok ，收支平衡<br />\n一人獨資十幾萬<br />\n反而人事問題先最擾人</blockquote><br />\n巴打公司幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你平時點做宣傳"},{"pid":"bad464caa803c59b4d9aaf8e9fd895e0669edd4e","tid":437963,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭唔駛蝕已經好好啦，慢慢再諗點做上去</blockquote><br />\n我有時都咁同自己講<br />\n但眼見身邊打工啲fd個個好似好好景咁<br />\n有時問起我收入真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c92ea6f54f0add2f2e4af4a971bac85c495069a","tid":437963,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留意細節好緊要 同埋要用心</blockquote><br />\n努力中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47a9d75cbae891158c8426585cc6e6a77c6e129","tid":4